{"tid":1395752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁競徽八一建軍節發文「送上特別敬意」　內地網民激讚：香港希望","createTime":"2019-08-02T00:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T00:46:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3233333bd08784c7f56924ec2ad5dab862b309d","tid":1395752,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3108569/org/df7b0fe1ccade4b571a1faaba7d21163.jpg/vc4T6g4HaJk0sV7iVuxaLr0IlKckZeUPBonC7QaJwu0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3108569%2Forg%2Fdf7b0fe1ccade4b571a1faaba7d21163.jpg%2Fvc4T6g4HaJk0sV7iVuxaLr0IlKckZeUPBonC7QaJwu0&h=3e797bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少內地網民都話估到唯唯今日一定會發文祝賀八一建軍節。<br />\n<br />\n今日係中國建軍節，一班熱愛祖國嘅藝人當然要表心跡。早前因「被參加」遊行而怒刪IG嘅梁競徽 （前名：梁烈唯），今早在微博上載紅底白字「81」圖片，並發文表白「在這個特別的日子，送上特別的敬意」並附了加油的公仔打氣，值得一提，梁競徽仍然係用緊華為手機，身體力行表現出愛祖國用國貨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3108516/org/a8ef4d9ca03ef6226c0b4709ebf3c2e4.png/hWxhG5IHT2AvQsrsoKMfPrB3xTnjoZ3xOWs_MzlrPzM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3108516%2Forg%2Fa8ef4d9ca03ef6226c0b4709ebf3c2e4.png%2FhWxhG5IHT2AvQsrsoKMfPrB3xTnjoZ3xOWs_MzlrPzM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=510a86de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯唯熱烈祝賀八一建軍節。<br />\n<br />\n對於梁競徽呢種高尚嘅愛國情懷，唔少網民都表示讚好，亦紛紛留言叮囑佢要注意安全，亦有留言表示「香港現在這樣子，你是公開藝人還這樣支持，真係好捧」、「你這樣三觀正的藝人，才是香港未來的希望」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3108620/org/e5edf11e80aa228e6efaa48486102935.jpg/p1rjrejT077coYJeeziC0fMa_PndQiUchqnVuoap1bo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3108620%2Forg%2Fe5edf11e80aa228e6efaa48486102935.jpg%2Fp1rjrejT077coYJeeziC0fMa_PndQiUchqnVuoap1bo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=920e004a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫兆倫都有向祖國表心跡。<br />\n<br />\n而同樣都係愛國之星嘅溫兆倫除轉發、讚好駐香港部隊隊官博影片外，更上載由佢作曲、作詞嘅《愛在戰火紛飛時》歌曲，完完全全感受到佢有幾愛國。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3108531/org/e20868c94abdd262b4c0034ea3d6308e.png/9JxcfcusaXV3W-eDzixjIr5HSC1j2BLrxpr1k8aa9ZM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3108531%2Forg%2Fe20868c94abdd262b4c0034ea3d6308e.png%2F9JxcfcusaXV3W-eDzixjIr5HSC1j2BLrxpr1k8aa9ZM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e3f675a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3年前曾為何君堯拉票嘅陳小春，今日在微博轉發了「駐香港部隊」微博的防暴演練短片，並發文表示：「八一建軍節快樂」。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：鄺鈺瑩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/359000/%E6%A2%81%E7%AB%B6%E5%BE%BD%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%BB%8D%E7%AF%80%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%95%AC%E6%84%8F-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F359000%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E5%2585%25AB%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2596%2587-%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E6%2595%25AC%25E6%2584%258F-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25BF%2580%25E8%25AE%259A-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=9a8866e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/359000/%E6%A2%81%E7%AB%B6%E5%BE%BD%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%BB%8D%E7%AF%80%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87-%E9%80%81%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E6%95%AC%E6%84%8F-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B</a>"},{"pid":"5da5c778c4cecda1d023cf35565a178938de9bbf","tid":1395752,"uid":80303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:36:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推有用post<br />\non9藝人遲啲清算</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c